## Get Started

1. **Clone & install:**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-org/uatp-capsule-engine
cd uatp-capsule-engine/sdk/python
pip install -e .
```

2. **Start backend:**
```bash
cd ../..
./start_backend_dev.sh
```

3. **Make first decision auditable:**
```python
from uatp import UATP

client = UATP()
result = client.certify(
    task="Your AI task",
    decision="Your AI decision",
    reasoning=[{"step": 1, "thought": "Your reasoning", "confidence": 0.9}]
)
print(result.proof_url)
```

